org.apache.juneau.internal

Class SimpleMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractMap<String,Object>
      • org.apache.juneau.internal.SimpleMap
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Map<String,Object>

    public final class SimpleMap
extends AbstractMap<String,Object>
    An instance of a Map where the keys and values are simple String[] and Object[] arrays.

    Typically more efficient than HashMaps for small maps (e.g. <10 entries).

    Does not support adding or removing entries.

    Setting values overwrites the value on the underlying value array.
